# MindfulFlow

**An AI-powered mindful journaling and well-being app.**

MindfulFlow helps you reflect, celebrate wins, practice gratitude, and stay on track with your goals — all through a friendly AI companion named Aiden.

---

## Features

- **AI Journal** — Chat with Aiden, your empathetic AI companion, in a familiar messaging interface. One conversation per day, auto-saved in real time.
- **Ta-Done! List** — An accomplishment tracker designed to celebrate what you've done, not just what's left to do. Link items to your goals.
- **Gratitude Journal** — A simple space to record what you're grateful for each day.
- **Goal Tracker** — Set intentions and track their progress over time.
- **Insights & Search** — Ask questions about your past journal entries and discover patterns in your reflections.
- **Voice Input** — Speak your thoughts using built-in speech-to-text.
- **Time-Aware Prompts** — Aiden greets you with prompts that adapt to your time of day and timezone.
- **Custom Profile** — Upload a profile photo and set a display name.

---

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| Frontend | React + TypeScript (Vite) |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui |
| State Management | TanStack Query |
| Routing | Wouter |
| Backend | Node.js + Express (TypeScript) |
| Database | PostgreSQL via Drizzle ORM |
| AI | OpenAI GPT-4o |
| Auth | Replit Auth (OpenID Connect) |
| Sessions | express-session + connect-pg-simple |

